{"tid":505307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【何志平被捕】起訴書曝光涉8控罪 最高可判監85年罰款逾4,000萬","createTime":"2017-12-21T03:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T04:15:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"427bdefa37cf3f52e9e978d2d26e9979386c2379","tid":505307,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513824277_ddae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513824277_ddae.png&h=57f9a82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513821377_c33a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513821377_c33a.png&h=3e46416b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起訴表格詳列何志平的8項控罪及每項的最高刑罰，一旦全部罪成，何最高可被判監85年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513821381_e525.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513821381_e525.png&h=eb8b793b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何志平的代表律師月初為他申請保釋，提出以100萬美元擔保，當中包括25萬元現金及5人人事擔保，另加在家囚禁及電子監控作條件（黑框示），但最終申請都被法官拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》早前一連3日獨家報導何志平涉貪案，包括披露他過去9年穿梭各國的行蹤、為他向法庭陳情的擔保人身份、及他在美國的最後日程；何志平本周一正式被美國當局起訴，有關檔案亦隨之而被公開。最新公開的文件包括何志平起訴表格，當中列出每項控罪的最高刑罰；如8項控罪全部罪成，而刑期又分期執行，何志平最多可被判監85年及罰款港幣4,524萬。<br />\n<br />\n記者 林偉聰美國紐約報導<br />\n<br />\n起訴表格的被告資料一欄有何志平的名稱、囚禁地點、出生年份及代表律師名單，表格被詳列何志平被起訴的8項控罪、當中涉及的法例，及每項控罪的最高刑罰。何志平的控罪包括1項串謀違反《海外反腐敗法》（Foreign Corrupt Practice Act, FCPA）、4項違反《海外反腐敗法》、1項串謀洗錢、及2項洗錢罪。<br />\n<br />\n5項涉及《海外反腐敗法》的控罪每項均最高可判5年監禁，另加3年監外看管（supervised release）；3項涉及洗錢的控罪刑罰更重，每項最高可判監20年。換言之如果何志平全部控罪成立，法官又判處分期執行刑期，何最多可被判監85年。<br />\n<br />\n罰款方面，《海外反腐敗法》控罪最高罰款額由10萬至25萬美元不等，洗錢的最高罰款額則達50萬元，但全部控罪都有替代最高罰款額，設於控罪涉及金額的兩倍。以何志平涉作出合共290萬美元賄款計算，最高罰款為580美元，相等約港幣4,524萬。<br />\n<br />\n其他公開的文件包括早前報導的護照副本，顯示何志平過往9年共出訪30個國家，當中17個屬一帶一路國家，不少都是他背後的中國華信能源的業務所在地；另外亦包括其辯護律師為他撰寫的保釋申請信，披露了何被捕前原定的訪美行程。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608387&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZG0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=0a61c934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608387&h=b57f6930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171221/57608387</a>"},{"pid":"8feb51673dc854b062e4386c19f9c39e14e0362c","tid":505307,"uid":30633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:51:43.000Z","msg":"轉做污點證人，爆董大鑊"},{"pid":"0653911c8f4d56879459aed133523b46e5102f2e","tid":505307,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:57:26.000Z","msg":"Prison Architect 加埋佢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703eef1de07224f02d2d95ad9fac9c682ff81232","tid":505307,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T03:59:46.000Z","msg":"希望司法部成功向到佢入獄"},{"pid":"3d46e944d680e00028f152003285eff6e26778d3","tid":505307,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Prison Architect 加埋佢落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c4fc71433cc72e038fecc3c689fb96fd381e9f","tid":505307,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:11:54.000Z","msg":"保外就醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src